data.description: Best in class!! Stunning 5  bedroom home with backyard paradise. Over 3700 sf home with heated swimming pool and spa surrounded by lush landscaping. Excellent home for entertaining and family gatherings. 3 full baths and 1 half bath. Primary bedroom down, 3 bedrooms up. Tile and custom wood floors thru-out. Large game room up, private study and both formals. Gourmet kitchen with loads of cabinets for the chef of the house. Huge 3 car detached garage and retractable awning for outdoor shade. Many updates including fresh paint, LED lighting, heated pool, cabinets upgrades, frameless primary glass shower door and so many more. Excellent Humble schools and close to ample shopping
